<h2>Actions to Develop Fractions Understanding</h2>

<p>The seven mathematics processes – problem solving, reasoning and proving, reflecting, selecting tools
and computational strategies, connecting, representing, and communicating – are integral to meaningful
learning of fractions.</p>

